”</strong>字样。虽然没有透露明确的信息，但该玩家似乎是一名充当 VTuber 的分销商。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/08/pastedimage0-1fe98d211b70e070bbbf79af3fe5444a-kix.ls7s3eisst1o.png" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/08/pastedimage0-1fe98d211b70e070bbbf79af3fe5444a-kix.ls7s3eisst1o-1024x570.png"></a><br /> （来自<a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/2314720/Chillas_Art_Parasocial/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Parasocial Steam 页面</a>）</p><p> PV以明亮的旋律开始，这对于<a href="https://twitter.com/ChillasArt" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Chiraz Art</a>的作品来说是不寻常的，但到了后半段，它变成了令人不安的元素，比如便利店里可疑男子的视角、对讲机的铃声响起等。入口处等等。你也许能够体验到潜伏在主播日常生活中的恐惧。</p><p>单击此处查看“Parasocial”的 Steam 分发目的地。<br /> <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/2314720/Chillas_Art_Parasocial/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://store.steampowered.com/app/2314720/Cillas_Art_Parasocial/</a> </p><div class="mg-mogura-card m-0 mb-2 mb-md-3"><div class="d-flex"><div class="mg-mogura-card-thumb position-relative"><img class="mg-img-cover position-absolute h-100 w-100" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2020/02/202002261931604000-300x169.jpg"></div><div class="card-body mg-card-text p-2 p-lg-3"><h3 class="h6 mt-0 mw-0 mb-1 p-0 card-title mg-card-title mg-text-break-all text-dark font-weight-normal">恐怖游戏《夜班事件》在VTuber中热潮 尖叫吓人送</h3><div class="text-gray mg-mogura-card-excerpt mb-1 my-md-2">2月下旬左右开始，恐怖游戏《夜班事件》在VTuber中掀起一股热潮。 《夜班事件》讲述了一名女大学生深夜在便利店打工的故事。</div> <span class="badge badge-outline-live mg-mogura-card-badge px-2">VTuber</span> <span class="text-muted small ml-1">2020.02.26</span> </div></div></div><div class="mg-mogura-card m-0 mb-2 mb-md-3"><div class="d-flex"><div class="mg-mogura-card-thumb position-relative"><img class="mg-img-cover position-absolute h-100 w-100" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/06/2023_06_19_15_11_17_6735-300x169.png"></div><div class="card-body mg-card-text p-2 p-lg-3"><h3 class="h6 mt-0 mw-0 mb-1 p-0 card-title